media:group.media:title: [TAS] INSANE Canyon Dribble Hardcore 100% 3:23 (-52:00 RTA)
media:group.media:description:
This is a tool-assisted speedrun of the canyon dribble map in hardcore mode. No physics were altered. The ball and car position only get set at the very start of the run. It's simply a combination of exact inputs that leads to this result.

Uploaded on April 1st with the following description:
I've been speedrunning this custom Rocket League map a bit lately and got this insane run. I will have a proper video coming out tomorrow that will explain how I got so good at speedrunnning. The fastest previous time I was able to find was from Fairy Peak on his first try (55:23). There is an any % run with 1:34 but that obviously skips all the checkpoints.

Map by Ebarra0 https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2697227168
